<title>BP says resumes activity at Gulf spill site</title>
<source>Reuters</source>
<date>2010-08-13</date>
<snippet>NEW YORK, Aug 13 - BP <BP.L> said it had resumed activity at the Gulf of Mexico spill site that had been suspended due to the storm. ...</snippet>
<content>
        
    
NEW YORK Aug 13 (Reuters) - BP (BP.L) said it had resumed
activity at the Gulf of Mexico spill site that had been
suspended due to the storm.

 The company said that its storm packer had been released
and was being pulled to the surface as the threat of storm
passes. (Reporting by Janet McGurty).




